{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Metaball"], "type": "title", "extent": [35, 48], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [48, 93], "text": ["Creates metaballs and metasurfaces. "]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [93, 275], "text": ["This tool is useful for modeling blob-like things that mold together, such as rain drops puddling. It can also be used to create organic shapes, or as a force field such a tornado."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [368, 480], "text": ["Click the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/metaball", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "SOP/metaball"}, " ", {"text": ["Metaball"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/metaball", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/metaball"}, " tool on the ", {"text": ["Create"], "type": "ui"}, " tab."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "extent": [566, 668], "text": ["You can hold ", {"keys": ["Alt"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " to detach the metaball from the construction plane."]}], "indent": 12, "role": "item", "extent": [548, 566], "container": true, "type": "note"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "note_group"}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Move the cursor into the ", {"text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/views/3dview"}, ". "], "extent": [480, 548], "container": true, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [763, 868], "text": ["If you press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " without clicking, Houdini places the metaball at the origin."]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Click ", {"keys": ["LMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " to place the metaball anywhere in the ", {"text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/views/3dview"}, ". "], "extent": [668, 763], "container": true, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord"}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Place the metaball anywhere in the scene"], "role": "item", "extent": [311, 368], "container": true, "type": "task"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [912, 1037], "text": ["Press ", {"keys": ["Ctrl", "LMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " on the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/metaball", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "SOP/metaball"}, " ", {"text": ["Metaball"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/metaball", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/metaball"}, " tool on the ", {"text": ["shelf"], "fullpath": "/shelf/index", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/shelf/"}, "."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Place the metaball at the origin"], "role": "item", "extent": [868, 912], "container": true, "type": "task"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "task_group"}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1037, 1494], "text": ["If you are at the geometry level or have an object selected and you create a ", {"text": ["metaball"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/metaball", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/metaball"}, ", it will go into the selected object. If you are at the scene level and create a metaball, the viewer and the ", {"text": ["network editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/network", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/panes/network"}, " will switch to the geometry level of the selected object. This unique feature allows you to merge multiple metaballs together automatically by creating them sequentially and close together."]}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1494, 1542], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/images/shelf/metaball.png", "scheme": "Image", "type": "link", "value": "/images/shelf/metaball.png"}]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1553, 1744], "text": ["Metaballs can be moved once they are placed by either dragging them in the ", {"text": ["scene 